Level 56 mage. Start in the hallway behind the main fighting room for frenzy. Make and buff pet. Turn the corner and pull first wander, quickly kill. Don't bother with the other spawn in the hole sorta thing. Just run past into the small little hallway right before Frenzy room itself. Should be a spawn sitting in that hall way. Let pet make quick work of it. Then med to full and buff up. <br>
Now pulling can be tricky. I don't know if I pulled singals due to my level or not. But I did. I pulled right spawn first. Then med'ed. Then pulled left spawn. Then had pet kill middle. Ofcourse I split them up a bit as to spread the spawn time on them. It because quiet easy once you have it down. You can even pull sent once you start timers etc. Becarefull with Sent he has ALOT of hp =p. I used Chain cast on sent. <br>
